Carlita introduces an audio version of the worldwide banned documentary on the now much limited &amp; monitored Youtube called "The Freedom Movie 2". What makes this audio version especially unique is that Carlita quotes the written texts that could be read on the visual format throughout the two hour documentary that were shown in the video.   "Whether we are aware of it or not, the whole of humanity is subconsciously grieving the loss of our Sovereign Freedom. Everything going on in the world, is and has always been a mere reflection of what is existing inside of ourselves. Many people remain in denial of the problems of the human psyche,just as they are in denial of the massive conspiracy to enslave humanity, to stop the robbery of the evolution of the humankind, we all must individually come to a new understanding about life. The understanding that the conspiracy causing the threat to the continuation of human existence &amp;  the illness in our minds is one of the same."
